教程6: 综合分析1-Chromatin activity和Motif score评估¶

在前面scBasset的分析中，我们已经得到了每一个转录因子TF的Motif富集分数，并保存在了data/scbasset/atac_motif_act.h5ad路径下，在本节教程中，我们将学习如何从scATAC-seq数据中得到Chromatin activity，并结合Motif score与前面分析的RNA expression进行三个维度的评估

1. Chromatin activity¶

我们从cellranger-atac的输出中得到了filtered_peak_bc_matrix.h5文件，在染色质活性分数的评估中，我们将使用MAESTRO来计算，关于MAESTRO的详细介绍请看官方文档。

但与官方文档不同的是，我们这里使用的是T2TCHM13的参考基因组，MAESTRO的官方文档里没有，所以我们需要对MAESTRO的文件进行一些修改。我已经向官方提交了PR，但是官方还没同意我的合并。具体的修改内容可以参照我的PR：https://github.com/liulab-dfci/MAESTRO/pull/165/files

参考代码如下

MAESTRO scatac-genescore \
--format h5 \
--peakcount /home/leihu/data/analysis/rb_tutorial/data/cellranger-atac/SRR13633766/filtered_peak_bc_matrix.h5 \
--genedistance 10000 \
--species T2TCHM13 \
--model Enhanced \
-d /home/leihu/data/analysis/rb_tutorial/data/geneactivity \
--outprefix SRR13633766_CHM13

参考输出结果如下

peaks number:  234628
peaks number in gene promoters and exons:  40786
peaks number out gene promoters and exons: 193842

我们将SRR13633766与SRR13633772分别生成一个基因活性矩阵，然后由于MAESTRO的输出格式是.h5，我们需要改成h5ad，在这里我们需要注意的是，这个.h5格式不是常见的.h5py格式，所以我们需要自己构建一个新的读取函数

import os
import collections
import tables
import h5py
import scipy.io
import csv
import gzip
import scipy.sparse as sp_sparse
import argparse as ap
import pandas as pd
FeatureBCMatrix = collections.namedtuple('FeatureBCMatrix', ['ids', 'names', 'barcodes', 'matrix'])
def read_10X_h5(filename):
    """Read 10X HDF5 files, support both gene expression and peaks."""
    with tables.open_file(filename, 'r') as f:
        try:
            group = f.get_node(f.root, 'matrix')
        except tables.NoSuchNodeError:
            print("Matrix group does not exist in this file.")
            return None
        feature_group = getattr(group, 'features')
        ids = getattr(feature_group, 'id').read()
        names = getattr(feature_group, 'name').read()
        barcodes = getattr(group, 'barcodes').read()
        data = getattr(group, 'data').read()
        indices = getattr(group, 'indices').read()
        indptr = getattr(group, 'indptr').read()
        shape = getattr(group, 'shape').read()
        matrix = sp_sparse.csc_matrix((data, indices, indptr), shape=shape)
        return FeatureBCMatrix(ids, names, barcodes, matrix)
import os import collections import tables import h5py import scipy.io import csv import gzip import scipy.sparse as sp_sparse import argparse as ap import pandas as pd FeatureBCMatrix = collections.namedtuple('FeatureBCMatrix', ['ids', 'names', 'barcodes', 'matrix']) def read_10X_h5(filename): """Read 10X HDF5 files, support both gene expression and peaks.""" with tables.open_file(filename, 'r') as f: try: group = f.get_node(f.root, 'matrix') except tables.NoSuchNodeError: print("Matrix group does not exist in this file.") return None feature_group = getattr(group, 'features') ids = getattr(feature_group, 'id').read() names = getattr(feature_group, 'name').read() barcodes = getattr(group, 'barcodes').read() data = getattr(group, 'data').read() indices = getattr(group, 'indices').read() indptr = getattr(group, 'indptr').read() shape = getattr(group, 'shape').read() matrix = sp_sparse.csc_matrix((data, indices, indptr), shape=shape) return FeatureBCMatrix(ids, names, barcodes, matrix)

import re
import anndata
for h_n in srr_paths:
    print(h_n)
    scatac_count=read_10X_h5(current_path+'data/geneactivity/'+h_n)
    peakmatrix = scatac_count.matrix
    features = scatac_count.names.tolist()
    features = [re.sub("\W", "_", feature.decode()) for feature in features]
    features = [feature.encode() for feature in features]
    barcodes = scatac_count.barcodes.tolist()
    adata=anndata.AnnData(peakmatrix.T,obs=barcodes,var=features)
    adata.obs.index=[i.decode('utf-8') for i in adata.obs[0]]
    adata.var.index=[i.decode('utf-8') for i in adata.var[0]]
    del adata.obs[0]
    del adata.var[0]
    adata.write_h5ad(current_path+'data/geneactivity/'+h_n.replace('score.h5','mact.h5ad'),compression='gzip')

3. 多组学特征分析¶

在前面的分析，我们已经得到了RNA，ATAC，ACTIVITY和MOTIF SCORE四个层次的数据，在这里，我们需要分析每个组学层的特征，寻找共同点。我们首先对ACTIVITY与MOTIF进行降维可视化。
